\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:07:56.000Z","msg":"但好明顯條月供成係賺唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d7fb9e897d8ae519fc66412d84ded827acc414","tid":2369362,"uid":242846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a663d0cf76777e860a8bcd702d2fc638bfe2adb","tid":2369362,"uid":57767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:50:51.000Z","msg":"睇你性格，有啲人技術分析搵到錢，長線搵唔到錢，有啲就相反<br />\n<br />\n同埋睇你賺錢既定義係啲乜，如果諗住一個月賺幾萬蚊，兩者都有可能<br />\n<br />\n但如果去到基金大戶要嬴數以億計，我只可以話得長線係做到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:08:12.000Z","msg":"基金大戶個倉咁大，自然會分開長線同短線，唔會做死同一隻，要做到每年穩定回報基本上都要靠短炒配合<br />\n但係散戶長揸的確係最容易贏錢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ba228a3f08a05dc1b74fea969763c766f66e99","tid":2369362,"uid":221797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f47dc3a4dccc107ccf196663feba0e7a3717bfc4","tid":2369362,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T05:59:19.000Z","msg":"股海巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你d片好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T08:05:10.000Z","msg":"多謝月下巴"},{"pid":"5486f9d39c730559655c0367e83a6df11cfc7917","tid":2369362,"uid":221797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d244b675608aaa946897114df7b0e1d4d9dea38","tid":2369362,"uid":264974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:04:33.000Z","msg":"一下子就抹殺技術分析嘅價值，等於leaving free money on the table"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T08:07:17.000Z","msg":"雖然近排沽空Tesla 瀨野，但是Michael Burry （《大賣空》的主角原型）在進行基本分析後，在進場時都會以技術分析考慮買入/沽空位置"},{"pid":"3a16e56c919b54b58f4bb05c7c3eaef18bd45877","tid":2369362,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci